data.description: Restore this vintage gem to its former glory! Located on an oversized corner lot, opposite the levee in Harahan, this spacious 6-bed, 3-bath home exudes mid-century modern charm. Original terrazzo floors, a sunken living room, and vintage bathrooms are just a glimpse of its potential. This sturdy brick home features a 5-year-old roof, roll-down storm shutters, off-street parking for 5 cars, rear yard vehicle access, a covered patio, and a large garage with indoor bbq pit/pizza oven and additional half bath. The layout is already perfect. House has never flooded and resides in Flood Zone X. Sold AS IS, seller will make no repairs or concessions.
